name: White Roost Canyon (Main Fork)
description:
Introduction

White Roost is a nice Half Day pulldown with three Raps up to 75ft. and and nice hike through a varnished canyon. There is a slick rock exit which will take you back to the Plateau so this can be done as a loop with no car shuttle necessary.
